getHighestSortedAndExclude

protected static List<Card> getHighestSortedAndExclude(int noof,
                                                       List<Card> cards,

Sorts the list of cards by Rank in descending order and removes any occurrences of cards in the list of excluded cards. Example: getHighestSortedAndExclude(2, {5d, 9c, Jd, 2c, Qs}, {Qs, 9c}) Result: {Jd, 5d}

Parameters:
noof - The max length of the resulting list of cards
cards -
exclude - A list of cards to exclude from the result
Returns:
A descending (by Rank) list of cards

getLongestConsecutiveSubset

protected static List<Card> getLongestConsecutiveSubset(List<Card> cards)
Returns the longest possible list of cards in Rank order. A card ranked ACE can be both at the beginning of a list or at the end. If no consecutive list can be found in the list of cards an empty list is returned. Example: getLongestConsecutiveSubset({5h, 3s, Ad, As, 2c, Kh, 4c}) Returns: {Ad, 2c, 3s, 4c, 5h}

Parameters:
cards -
Returns:
The longest consecutive sublist of cards found or the empty list if none found.

removeDuplicatesByRankAndSortByRank

protected static List<Card> removeDuplicatesByRankAndSortByRank(List<Card> cards)
Sorts the list of cards by Rank and then removes any cards of the same Rank. Example: removeDuplicatesByRankAndSortByRank({5h, Jd, 3s, 5d, Js} Returns: {3s, 5d, Jd}

Parameters:
cards -
Returns:
A sorted list of Cards with no duplicate Ranks.

getHighestOfSameRankExcluding

protected static List<Card> getHighestOfSameRankExcluding(int noof,
                                                          List<Card> cards,
                                                          Rank excludedRank)
Searches a List of Cards for cards of the same rank that exist in least noof times and returns the highest ranking list, excluded any Card of the excluded Rank.

Parameters:
noof - The minimum number of cards of same rank
cards - The list of cards available
excludedRank - A rank to exclude from the result
Returns:
A list of cards of noof length of the highest rank.
